♪ Call the cops
who got all the drugs ♪

28:09.688 --> 28:11.994
♪ And then send them home
by noon... ♪

28:12.038 --> 28:13.822
Ica...

28:13.866 --> 28:15.345
♪ Oh, well, let it burn,
let it burn ♪

28:17.783 --> 28:19.175
♪ Rebellious attitude

28:19.219 --> 28:20.481
