28:20.524 --> 28:21.830
♪ We can't do nothing right

28:21.874 --> 28:23.179
♪ When wrong it what we do

28:23.223 --> 28:25.051
♪ 'Cause we die to live

28:25.094 --> 28:26.574
♪ We die to live

28:28.315 --> 28:31.013
♪ We ain't got the time
for a Christian lullaby ♪

28:31.057 --> 28:32.188
♪ When off goes the alarm

28:32.232 --> 28:33.537
♪ And the house is going down

28:33.581 --> 28:36.192
♪ We die to live,
we die to live ♪

28:38.107 --> 28:39.500
♪ We could go all night

28:39.543 --> 28:40.849
♪ Till the morning light...

28:42.111 --> 28:44.026
Hey, ugly.

28:44.070 --> 28:45.593
Incendia.

28:49.075 --> 28:50.772
♪ Let it burn

28:50.816 --> 28:53.862
♪ Oh, let it burn,
let it burn... ♪

28:53.906 --> 28:55.516
ALARIC:
New theory.

28:55.559 --> 28:56.517
Cyclops.

28:56.560 --> 28:58.258
Yeah.♪ Oh

28:58.301 --> 29:01.217
♪ well, let it burn,
let it burn. ♪

29:14.665 --> 29:16.319
Ugh.

29:16.363 --> 29:18.408
You think it's really a...?

29:24.023 --> 29:25.981
Yep.

29:26.025 --> 29:27.766
Great.

29:27.809 --> 29:30.377
Let's get out of here.

29:54.096 --> 29:56.403
Hey, Lizzie. How'd the spell go?

29:56.446 --> 29:58.884
You're not gonna
believe this.

29:58.927 --> 30:00.799
I have something
to tell you, too.
Okay.

30:00.842 --> 30:03.279
Well, me first, 'cause I want
you to hear it from me.

30:03.323 --> 30:06.456
So, that spell that you were
helping me with earlier?

30:06.500 --> 30:08.197
I know you probably
don't want to hear this,

30:08.241 --> 30:09.677
but it was to help me find

30:09.720 --> 30:11.940
this mystery guy
I've been looking for.

30:11.984 --> 30:16.423
And I-I don't want
to hurt your feelings, but...

30:16.466 --> 30:20.166
I think I have a crush on him.

30:22.995 --> 30:24.866
When I was in Europe,

30:24.910 --> 30:27.477
it was so amazing

30:27.521 --> 30:30.480
because nobody knew who I was.

30:30.524 --> 30:33.179
I was just
this brand-new person.

30:33.222 --> 30:35.094
I could start over.

30:35.137 --> 30:38.967
I wasn't "Crazy Lizzie."

30:39.011 --> 30:41.230
I was just me.

30:42.492 --> 30:44.973
And when Sebastian
looked at me today,

30:45.017 --> 30:47.715
I-I felt that way again.

30:47.758 --> 30:51.240
He doesn't know
anything about me.

30:51.284 --> 30:53.764
I can start over.

30:53.808 --> 30:57.246
So, thank you

30:57.290 --> 30:59.858
for helping.

31:02.425 --> 31:04.819
I should've told you.

31:13.219 --> 31:15.656
What are friends for?

31:21.227 --> 31:25.013
Wait. What were you
gonna say?

31:25.057 --> 31:27.929
Uh, just that, uh...

31:31.890 --> 31:35.894
...it was really nice
to see you happy today.

31:48.254 --> 31:50.125
ALARIC:
That was some
nice work back there.

31:51.779 --> 31:55.348
Surprising amount of overlap
between troll and cyclops.

31:55.391 --> 31:57.350
Yeah, there really is. Yeah.

31:58.742 --> 32:03.443
Look, I, uh, I know
you're not gonna stay.

32:08.013 --> 32:09.188
Here.

32:09.231 --> 32:11.930
♪ I crossed the last line...

32:11.973 --> 32:14.323
Take it.

32:14.367 --> 32:17.587
♪ She shattered that land...

32:17.631 --> 32:19.067
Be safe out there.

32:19.111 --> 32:22.288
You're good at this, you know?

32:22.331 --> 32:24.638
Monster hunting?

32:27.119 --> 32:29.295
Helping kids.

32:29.338 --> 32:32.994
Ah.

32:33.038 --> 32:35.910
You should keep the beard.

32:38.739 --> 32:41.481
♪ I could drink her away

32:45.528 --> 32:50.490
♪ I hit the bottom,
get carried away ♪

32:53.623 --> 32:57.888
♪ Oh, I can't stand up
straight... ♪

32:57.932 --> 33:00.326
Hey.

33:00.369 --> 33:02.023
♪ Please take me home...

33:02.067 --> 33:03.198
Hey.

33:03.242 --> 33:06.245
We saw each other
earlier, right?

33:06.288 --> 33:10.031
Yeah. Uh...

33:10.075 --> 33:12.947
I was just out on a walk
to clear my head.

33:12.991 --> 33:14.166
Rough night?

33:14.209 --> 33:17.299
Uh, yeah, actually, uh...

33:17.343 --> 33:20.215
Relationship trouble.

33:20.259 --> 33:22.348
Must be contagious.

33:22.391 --> 33:23.958
Why? You, too?

33:24.002 --> 33:26.613
Yeah. I'm with this
really amazing girl,

33:26.656 --> 33:29.007
but all of a sudden,
everything's super complicated.

33:29.050 --> 33:30.312
Huh.

33:30.356 --> 33:32.140
You?

33:32.184 --> 33:34.142
Oh, uh...

33:36.536 --> 33:40.148
Uh, old story, I guess, uh...

33:40.192 --> 33:42.846
Fell for a guy who doesn't
even know that I exist.

33:42.890 --> 33:44.022
Huh.

33:44.065 --> 33:45.501
That's classic.

33:45.545 --> 33:48.156
Yeah.

33:48.200 --> 33:50.376
She is really great,

33:50.419 --> 33:53.553
but I just feel like
I want it to be perfect,

33:53.596 --> 33:55.946
and...
Yeah.

33:55.990 --> 33:57.992
...and I want to be
the perfect boyfriend,

33:58.036 --> 34:01.213
and she's trying to be
the perfect girlfriend,

34:01.256 --> 34:05.304
and it was really effortless,
but now it feels so...

34:05.347 --> 34:09.090
off. I don't know.

34:09.134 --> 34:12.398
Sorry.
No, uh...

34:14.574 --> 34:16.663
You know, um,

34:16.706 --> 34:18.708
a very smart boy
once taught me

34:18.752 --> 34:20.449
that sometimes
you have to be

34:20.493 --> 34:23.931
brave enough to be
imperfect with people...

34:25.411 --> 34:28.370
...even if it's scary.

34:28.414 --> 34:29.893
Yeah.

34:29.937 --> 34:33.071
♪ Please take me home...

34:34.942 --> 34:37.031
Of course, you're gonna
have to take your own advice

34:37.075 --> 34:40.295
and tell that boy of yours
that you exist.
Uh...

34:40.339 --> 34:42.210
Oh.

34:42.254 --> 34:44.125
I don't know about that.

34:45.866 --> 34:48.912
♪ Lay me down,
close the blinds... ♪

34:48.956 --> 34:51.132
I hope your night gets better.

34:51.176 --> 34:53.743
Thanks.
This'll help.

34:53.787 --> 34:56.746
Peanut butter blast,
whipped cream on the bottom.

34:56.790 --> 34:59.880
It's probably all melted by now,
but, um...

34:59.923 --> 35:01.925
Oh.

35:01.969 --> 35:03.318
I don't even know
why I ordered it.

35:03.362 --> 35:05.712
I didn't have of it.
I didn't want a milkshake.

35:05.755 --> 35:07.583
It just seemed...

35:07.627 --> 35:10.978
♪ Baby, please take me home

35:13.459 --> 35:15.765
♪ I'm tired of running...

35:15.809 --> 35:17.593
Thanks for listening.

35:17.637 --> 35:20.161
♪ Take me home♪

35:20.205 --> 35:22.163
♪ Take me home

35:22.207 --> 35:23.947
♪ Take me home♪

35:23.991 --> 35:27.560
♪ Don't leave me
out in the cold ♪

35:27.603 --> 35:30.258
♪ Someone please take me home.

35:39.224 --> 35:41.574
JOSIE:
Come in.

35:46.709 --> 35:47.884
♪ Loneliness

35:47.928 --> 35:51.279
♪ Is at his senses...

35:54.326 --> 35:58.591
I'm sorry.

36:00.114 --> 36:02.682
We shouldn't even have gone out
if you were getting sick.

36:02.725 --> 36:05.032
I'm not sick.

36:07.252 --> 36:09.645
I'm allergic to seaweed.

36:09.689 --> 36:13.301
But sushi is, like, all seaweed.

36:15.260 --> 36:17.479
And you ate it anyway?

36:17.523 --> 36:19.916
Why?
Um...

36:19.960 --> 36:23.268
because you seemed like
you really wanted sushi.

36:23.311 --> 36:27.228
I didn't want to be a problem
on our first date.

36:27.272 --> 36:29.665
Why would that
be a problem?
Um...

36:29.709 --> 36:33.103
Because I'm always
the caretaker.

36:33.147 --> 36:37.369
And today just
really freaked me out

36:37.412 --> 36:40.198
because you didn't
need me at all.

36:41.808 --> 36:43.201
And if I'm not fixing problems,

36:43.244 --> 36:46.160
I have no idea
where I belong in your life.

36:46.204 --> 36:47.988
So I was stupid

36:48.031 --> 36:51.426
and I was jealous
because I'm just afraid

36:51.470 --> 36:53.733
that there's no place for me.

36:53.776 --> 36:58.259
And that's just how I am

36:58.303 --> 37:00.696
with boys, girls.

37:00.740 --> 37:02.045
Apparently, I'm just

37:02.089 --> 37:04.874
always codependent
and ridiculous.

37:04.918 --> 37:06.659
Or you've just never
been in a relationship

37:06.702 --> 37:09.662
where what
you want matters.

37:11.751 --> 37:14.362
Besides, you're not
the only ridiculous one.

37:14.406 --> 37:15.842
Pretty sure I'm a fraud.

37:15.885 --> 37:19.019
I mean, everyone says
I stopped Malivore,

37:19.062 --> 37:21.674
but all I did was wake up
next to an empty pit.

37:21.717 --> 37:24.067
I have no idea
what happened,

37:24.111 --> 37:28.376
only that I'm not
the hero they think I am.

37:28.420 --> 37:33.207
I went along with it
because it felt nice.

37:33.251 --> 37:35.078
I enjoyed it.

37:35.122 --> 37:38.517
I finally felt
like I belonged here.

37:39.953 --> 37:43.261
And most of all, um,

37:43.304 --> 37:47.221
